    "Furthermore, in domestic settings, emotionally intelligent robots are emerging as adaptive home assistants capable of recognizing and responding to user emotions and decoding human commands.",
    "These applications demonstrate the significant potential of HRI to transform everyday interactions and operational efficiencies across varied sectors.Overall, this review provides valuable insights and directions for the field of HRI, laying a solid foundation for future studies.",
    "We have identified key modalities for HRI, including control methods for human-robot collaboration, brain-computer interfaces for direct neurological commands, and the recognition of human emotions by robots.",
    "Additionally, our paper presents innovative methods to enhance multimodal HRI systems, incorporating brain signals and visual cues for more effective collaboration.",
    "By delving into current literature, we have highlighted the latest trends and emerging frontiers in the field."
